name: Aqua 'A'
description: Aqua A is a part of 36 days of type challenge. Where creators are asked to create all the letters and number for 36 days according to their own interpretation. So, my concept is about colors and places that resonates with each other. A depicts the aquamarine life, from little fish to hidden treasure beauties of marines. The monochromatic color palette takes to the under water life. Enjoy the magic of A.
